# o9ds Component Development

## Constraint

**Do not import or use any third-party UI/component libraries.**

- No MUI, Ant Design, Chakra, Radix UI, Headless UI, etc.
- Build all components from scratch.

## Allowed

- Native HTML elements
- Internal design tokens (from `index.css`, `tailwind.config.js`)
- Internal utility functions / hooks
- Utility libraries (classnames, date-fns, etc.) if approved — but **no UI component libraries**

## Goal

- Ensure consistency with o9 Design System
- Maintain full control over styling, behavior, and accessibility
- Avoid dependency on external UI frameworks

## Development Order

1. **Foundations first**: Set design tokens, spacing scale, typography, colors.
2. **Components second**: Build components using only those tokens — no libraries.
